snippet.title: Forged Battalion - Early Access Release Date Trailer (Steam)
snippet.description:
Forged Battalion goes into Early Access, January 16th 2018!
Follow and add to your wishlist on Steam: bit.ly/ForgedBattalion

Official website: https://www.team17.com/games/forged-battalion/
Follow Forged Battalion on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ForgedBattalion
Like Forged Battalion on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ForgedBattalion/
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/
Join us on Discord: http://discord.gg/team17

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Aven Colony, The Escapists, Genesis Alpha One, Overcooked, Sword Legacy: Omen, Yoku’s Island Express, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. Visit www.team17.com for more info.
